  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is:

        -  To define The differences of bio-chemical phenotypes in chronic airway inflammatory
           diseases.

        -  To identify novel biomarkers in chronic airway inflammatory diseases as a screening,
           diagnostic, or monitoring marker.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
